---+!! Gratia Release %CURRENT_RELEASE% (%RELEASE_DATE%)%BR% 


%TOC%

%STARTINCLUDE%
---+ Overview

The main purpose of this release (%CURRENT_RELEASE%) is to add support for authenticated connection between Probe and Collector.

---++Main Features:
   * SSL connection with Collector (from Probe and from other collector)
   * Implement StorageRecord in Collector, including summary table and Probe.

---++ BIRT Report Improvements:
   * Add ability to download the result of the modified query directly to csv file (i.e. without further manual intervention).

---++ Probe Improvements:

   * Add files ProxyUtil.py, GratiaPing.py to common package.
   * Secure upload to collector included self-signing.
   * MeterName -&gt; ProbeName (legacy name supported).
   * SOAPHost -&gt; CollectorHost (legacy name supported).
   * Probe-side record bundling.
   * Improve connection error handling.

---++ Misc.
   * Finalize RSV Probe monitoring Gratia.

---++ Email Reports
   * Per VO reporting name reports.
   * Turn on using recipient list from OIM for VO reports.

---++ Collector Improvements:
   * SSL connection with Collector (from Probe and from other collector)

---+++ Pending explicit request from Stakeholders.

---+++ Notices

---++ Additional Features:

